oul]] (credited as Julia Nickson) - [[List of Babylon 5 characters#Catherine Sakai|Catherine Sakai]] * [[Michael O'Hare]] - [[Jeffrey Sinclair]] * [[Robert Rusler]] - [[Warren Keffer]] * [[Robin Sachs]] - multiple roles * [[Mark Schneider (actor)|Mark Schneider]] - Wade * [[John Schuck]] - [[Draal]] * [[Tracy Scoggins]] - [[Elizabeth Lochley]] * [[Johnny Sekka]] - Dr. [[Benjamin Kyle]] * [[Kim Strauss]] - 10 characters * [[Patricia Tallman]] - [[Lyta Alexander]] * [[Marshall R. Teague|Marshall Teague]] - [[List of Babylon 5 characters#Ta.27Lon|Ta'Lon]] / Nelson Drake (6 episodes) * [[Andrea Thompson]] - [[Talia Winters]] * [[Tamlyn Tomita]] - [[Laurel Takashima]] * [[Louis Turenne]] - [[Brother Theo]] (and the original [[Draal]]) * [[John Vickery (actor)|John Vickery]] - [[Neroon]] (and Mr. Welles) * [[Ed Wasser]] - [[Morden (Babylon 5)|Morden]] (and Guerra) * [[Mary Woronov]] - [[List of Babylon 5 characters#Ko'Dath|Ko'Dath]] * [[Efrem Zimbalist, Jr.]] - [[List of Babylon 5 characters#William Edgars|William Edgars]]
